# UI Guidelines

Read `docs/UI_GUIDELINES.md`. Stack: Tailwind 4, shadcn/ui (base-nova), lucide-react, sonner.

## Colors

- Background: `bg-zinc-950`, cards: `bg-zinc-950` / `bg-zinc-900`
- Borders: `border-zinc-800` (panels), `border-zinc-900` (row dividers)
- Muted text: `text-zinc-500`, subtitles: `text-zinc-400`
- Brand accent: `bg-emerald-600` (active nav, CTAs)
- Use `cn()` from `@/lib/utils` for conditional classes

## Spacing

- Page: `p-8` (AppShell main), sections: `space-y-8`, cards: `p-6`
- Forms: `space-y-5`, tables: `px-6 py-4` header / `px-6 py-5` body

## Typography

- Eyebrow: `text-sm uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-zinc-500`
- Page title: `text-4xl font-bold`
- Section: `text-xl font-semibold`
- Table headers: `text-xs uppercase text-zinc-500`

## Radius

- Cards/tables: `rounded-2xl`
- Nav/buttons: `rounded-xl` / `rounded-lg`
- Avatars: `rounded-full`

## Components

- UI primitives: `@/components/ui/` (Button, Input, Select, Sheet, Badge, Card, Table)
- Icons: lucide-react only (`size={18}` tables, `h-4 w-4` buttons)
- Toasts: `toast.success()` / `toast.error()` — not `alert()`

## Tables

```tsx
<div className="overflow-hidden rounded-2xl border border-zinc-800 bg-zinc-950">
  <table className="w-full">
    <thead className="border-b border-zinc-800 bg-zinc-900">...</thead>
    <tr className="border-b border-zinc-900 hover:bg-zinc-900/60">...</tr>
  </table>
</div>
```

## Dialogs (Sheet)

```tsx
<Sheet open={open} onOpenChange={setOpen}>
  <SheetContent className="sm:max-w-lg">
    <SheetHeader><SheetTitle>...</SheetTitle></SheetHeader>
    <div className="mt-6"><Form onSuccess={() => setOpen(false)} /></div>
  </SheetContent>
</Sheet>
```

## Responsive

- Sidebar: `hidden lg:flex`
- Grids: `md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4`, `xl:grid-cols-3`
- UI copy in Russian

## Do Not

- Hardcode colors in `components/ui/` primitives (use CSS variables)
- Add domain logic to `components/ui/`
- Mix English/Russian in same view
